Title: [ANN] DENARO.IO - CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET AND WORLDWIDE DEBIT CARDS
Body: We do indeed, however, we offer unique features. For example, out payment terminals are a first for crypto. We also offer liquidity that is hard to rival, as you can use your Denaro debit card at ATMs and spend from it with millions of merchants worldwide.  Quote from: zayzik on February 22, 2018, 11:00:44 PM What can we do with tokens after ICO? You can take advantage of our token holder benefits (which you can read more about in our whitepaper - denaro.io/whitepaper), spend it with merchants, or, if you wanted to, you could sell the token for fiat or other cryptocurrencies.  Quote from: Kedril on February 22, 2018, 08:03:21 AM I recieved email with extra 25% bonus for buy, i entered coupon code and it said activated, but bonus still only 25%, not 50%. When you fix this? I want to buy 3000+ DNO. Thank you  Thank you for your question. The extra 25% bonus was part of our “first come, first served” contest. It is only the first 10 people to use the code that receive the bonus. We are sending out these emails every day. You have to try to be as fast as possible to cash in on the bonus. It changes each day- sometimes it is higher than 50%!  Quote from: nickbelski on February 23, 2018, 11:14:14 AM Your project and website looks very attractive in front, but when someone dig deeper, he can find some strange unsolved problems.  The most important thing is transparency. If your team members are real professionals and exist, they should have linkedin profiles. More than 20 days passed from the first enquiry about this problem, and it is not yet solved. Still No linkedin profiles on your site. Hi there, we appreciate your concern and apologize for the delay. We have been very busy recently but as this is a growing concern among our community, we will bring it nearer the top of our list of tasks and get it done as soon as possible. We do indeed have Linked In profiles and they will be added. If you want to find us in the meantime, you can search our names on Linked In followed by “Denaro”

Author: DENARO.IO
Title: [ANN] DENARO.IO - CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET AND WORLDWIDE DEBIT CARDS
Body: Hey! Thank you for your question. Denaro is a multi-crypto wallet system - it isn’t just a debit card. The payment terminals we offer are unique and a first mover in cryptocurrency. As for the card itself, its main advantage over BitPay is simply the fact it is compatible with BTC, LTC, ETH and DNO, whereas BitPay is only for Bitcoin. This adds unprecedented levels of liquidity to LTC and ETH, which is one of many reasons our debit card will have appeal from the get-go.  Other reasons include the fact that our wallet’s intuitive design provides unrivaled ease of use and that it is a one-stop shop for numerous cryptocurrencies. Instead of having to store, receive and spend different cryptocurrencies from different wallets, you can save yourself the hassle and store them all in one, user-friendly wallet that offers unparalleled liquidity both online and offline.

Author: DENARO.IO
Title: [ANN] DENARO.IO - CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET AND WORLDWIDE DEBIT CARDS
Body: There is no specific reason as to why we chose 3000DNO/ETH. In regards to exchanges, the DNO token will be listed on as many major exchanges as we can get it listed on. DNO’s primary purpose is to be used as a utility token - to drive all settlement on the network. It does indeed offer additional benefits/advantages, such as discounts when paying for merchant services, discounts on debit-card topups and a share of the transaction fees (distributed upon certain milestones being reached). You can learn more about the benefits of being a DNO token holder by reading our whitepaper (https://denaro.io/docs/Denaro_Whitepaper.pdf).  Quote from: KlifDonats on February 08, 2018, 11:51:53 AM How is the Denaro Wallet protected?  The Denaro wallet offers numerous layers of protection, which can all be activated from the security tab. These include IP-address protection, two-factor SMS authentication and two-factor email authentication. IP-address protection. When Denaro’s IP-address protection is enabled, your account is only accessible from the last IP address you successfully logged in from.  In addition to the Denaro account security, the tokens themselves are protected by our security algorithm; built on an Ethereum-blockchain protocol, DNO tokens possess secured hashing via smart contract and Private-Key Signatures (PKS) for instant and truly private transactions.  Quote from: douinaho on February 08, 2018, 07:00:46 PM a very satisfying result of your token sold out, then 17 hours waiting for ico opened, I can not wait for him. how long will ico run?  Indeed, exciting times are upon us. Thank you for your question. The ICO public sale will run for 35 days.

Author: DENARO.IO
Title: [ANN] DENARO.IO - CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET AND WORLDWIDE DEBIT CARDS
Body: 2,500,000 DNO tokens (2.5% of the total amount of DNO Token to be distributed) will be distributed over a 7-day period beginning on January 30, 2018 at 12:00 UTC and ending on February 6, 2018 at 11:59:59 UTC. 62,500,000 DNO tokens (62,5% of the total amount of DNO Token to be distributed) will be distributed over a 35-day period beginning on February 9, 2018 at 12:00 UTC and ending on March 15, 2018 at 11:59:59 UTC.  Quote from: btcyoda on January 31, 2018, 06:49:44 AM First of all, we have to get the answer is whether they had any tie-up with the banks because Tenx is also facing the same situation and they didn't get any approval from the bank for issuing the cards. Previously Visa has been canceled for cryptocurrency withdrawal.  We already have signed contracts with a card vendor. They will provide use with Mastercard debit cards. We understand how you have come to that belief, however, it is a misconception — VISA did not cancel cryptocurrency withdrawals, they canceled WaveCrest cards for violating their rules.  Quote from: wndrbr3d on January 31, 2018, 06:58:58 AM Denaro is just looking as one more "cryptocard" project. No any demonstation of real use. What are your advantages over such projects as TokenCard, Monaco, Fuzex, Tenx?  Now about team: where are links to Linkedin profiles for every team member? Only images we can see, no links at all... You can find this information in our whitepaper (over at https://denaro.io/) but our biggest competitive edge is the introduction of payment terminals for merchants so that they can accept debit cards and cryptocurrency using one unified device. Also, Denaro steers further clear of the herd of sheep by offering the option to receive bank transfers to your account using a personal IBAN number.  As for the team, we will be updating the information on our website within the next 24 hours. We understand how important transparency is and we apologise for the delay.

Author: olcaytu2005
Title: [ANN] DENARO.IO - CRYPTOCURRENCY WALLET AND WORLDWIDE DEBIT CARDS
Body: Website |  Whitepaper | Youtube | Bounty Thread | Twitter | Slack |  Facebook | Telegram   What is DENARO?  Denaro seamless payment ecosystem bridges the divide between cryptocurrencies and the mainstream market. The platform enables companies and individuals to send, spend, store, and exchange cryptos and fiat through secure web wallets, physical debit cards, merchant payment terminals, and IBAN.  LIQUIDITY  Denaro is a versatile payment solution that enable users to store, spend, and transfer their cryptocurrencies on an intuitive interface and debit card that addresses crypto’s number one problem — physically spending it. SECURITY  Denaro has developed secure and customizable SCI/APIs for merchant services that will facilitate the payments of goods and services online or offline using a web wallet or a physical debit card respectively. STORAGE  Tired of juggling all those ETH and BTC wallets? Utilising Denaro’s multi-cryptocurrency wallet, you no longer need multiple addresses. Not only does it allow you to receive and store multiple cryptocurrencies under one address, it also allows you to spend them at any ATM or store.    Explainer Video : What is Denaro    Advantages of Denaro For Merchants Securely receive payments in BTC, ETH, or DNO through customizable SCI/APIs without worrying about having to handle multiple wallet addresses. Instantaneous conversion of cryptos to BTC, ETH, or DNO and vice versa. Accept payments in fiat and instantly convert cryptocurrencies to fiat to hedge against volatility. Discounts and bonuses for merchants with volumes higher than $500,000, including; 1 free payment terminal and 50% off debit-card charges. An International Bank Account Number (IBAN) for receiving international transactions in fiat Personalized debit-card designs for merchants with high volumes.  For Users   Store, spend and send Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Denaro from a single user interface. Shop online and offline using a multi-cryptocurrency debit card. No additional fees for sending cryptocurrencies outside of the Denaro wallet; only network fees apply. An International Bank Account Number (IBAN) for receiving international transactions in fiat. Personalized debit-card designs for users with high volumes.  Pre-ICO  The Denaro private sale will offer DNO tokens to early contributors and investors to expedite platform development and facilitate the launch of the main/public token sale. The offer is scheduled as follows:  ● Supply: 2,500,000 ● Price: 3000 DNO/ETH ● Bonus: 25% ● Duration: 7 Days  Main-ICO  Denaro will offer the remaining 62,500,000 DNO tokens a month after the private sales. The soft cap for the main/public ICO is 10,000,000 DNO.  ● Minimum Contribution: $10 ● Maximum Contribution: $100,000 (for contributions larger than the maximum amount, please contact support@denaro.io for proper processing and bonus allocation) ● Bonus: Starting from 25% and decreasing throughout the token sale when certain milestones are hit ● Duration: 35 Days ● Referral Commission: 3%  ***This event is not open to contributors from the USA, China, and Singapore.      Note: I am making this Original Post for Denaro. I am not part of the project and point of contact. This thread will be manage by DENARO.IO
